Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.82,0:00:07.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I want to live in a world of peace\NWithout conflict, like the one I dreamed of.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.40,0:00:20.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I can't be patient any longer\NThere are things I must say
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.33,0:00:23.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,At the evening bus stop\Non the way home
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.49,0:00:26.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I Wave to those sunken shoulders,\NBye Bye Bye
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.09,0:00:32.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Got to show your Fighting Pose, Oh! Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.14,0:00:38.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That world I dreamed of\NIs peaceful every day, without any conflict.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.14,0:00:40.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But in reality,\Nthere are troubles every day
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.95,0:00:44.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And sometimes I regret,\Nthese Rolling days
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.73,0:00:55.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Lies probably have little meaning
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.59,0:01:02.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,~All my loving\NOtherwise, how can I go on?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.60,0:01:09.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A Sweet Love I dreamed of\NWhere lovers search for a hideaway
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.48,0:01:12.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But in reality,\Nthe days we can't meet
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.20,0:01:16.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Go on; but we still believe,\Nthese Rolling days
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.68,0:01:25.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We may stumble, but Way to go!!\NYeah!! Yeah!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.76,0:01:28.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A mud-caked Rolling star!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.30,0:01:58.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.47,0:01:59.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It’s the captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.79,0:02:01.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The captain is back!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.58,0:02:03.06,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.58,0:02:03.06,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.96,0:02:06.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.15,0:02:09.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’m fine.\NI brought down the Bount.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.46,0:02:15.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The South District is frozen over\Nfrom my Hyorinmaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.94,0:02:19.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It will melt shortly,\Nso go and retrieve the Bount.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.19,0:02:22.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Is it still alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.72,0:02:27.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No. I don’t know if there’s a corpse,\Nbut we can’t leave it there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.62,0:02:30.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Eventually, we’ll have to\Ngive it a burial.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.23,0:02:31.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.77,0:02:35.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Is Matsumoto back?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.67,0:02:39.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes sir! She’s with\NLieutenant Abarai of Squad 6,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.65,0:02:42.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,getting medical treatment for\Nthose who were injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.38,0:02:44.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Also, one more thing…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.93,0:02:45.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.90,0:02:48.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The Substitute Soul Reaper\Nis here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.59,0:02:49.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.06,0:02:56.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Captain…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.15,0:02:59.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.58,0:03:01.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What of the Bount?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.25,0:03:03.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I managed to take care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.43,0:03:04.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yo, Toshiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.96,0:03:07.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’m using your place.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.91,0:03:10.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You’re doing it on purpose,\Naren’t you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.33,0:03:13.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How many times must I tell you?\NIt’s Captain Hitsugaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.48,0:03:15.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What’s the big deal?\NIt doesn’t matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.75,0:03:16.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It does matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.27,0:03:19.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.75,0:03:24.83,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We happened to run into Rangiku\Nwhile chasing after Kariya.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.83,0:03:26.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.48,0:03:29.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ishida was hurt and we needed\Na place for him to rest,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.28,0:03:30.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,so it was perfect timing…!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.74,0:03:35.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Since we don’t have a home base\Nin Seireitei.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.39,0:03:38.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It was a stroke of good fortune that\Nwe met up with everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.14,0:03:41.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, we came uninvited like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.55,0:03:43.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, that’s the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.57,0:03:47.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I know it’s an inconvenience,\Nbut can you let us rest here a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.10,0:03:51.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.89,0:03:54.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ishida…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.00,0:03:56.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No… I’m okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.50,0:04:00.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Are you in pain?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.14,0:04:05.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I was the one who brought\Nthe Bounts to this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.89,0:04:10.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever injuries I incur,\NI’ll take full responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.89,0:04:14.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Inoue would know how to treat\Na wound like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.81,0:04:16.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It can’t be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.74,0:04:19.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Orihime is outside the walls\Nof Seireitei.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.15,0:04:23.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Due to the Bount invasion,\Nthere are injured all across Seireitei.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.79,0:04:26.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Squad 4 has their hands full.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.53,0:04:30.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But I’ve sent word, so someone\Nshould come in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.80,0:04:31.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You’ll be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.96,0:04:35.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You can’t fight,\Nbut your life is in no danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.79,0:04:37.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That won’t do!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.81,0:04:41.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I…came here to fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.01,0:04:43.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t be hasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.96,0:04:45.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We’ve gotten word that\NSoi Fon and Kurotsuchi
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.02,0:04:49.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,have taken down one Bount each.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.85,0:04:56.06,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Counting the one I brought down,\NKariya’s the only one left.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.24,0:04:58.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I must hand it to you, Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.64,0:05:02.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That metal doll gave us\Nso much trouble,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.25,0:05:04.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,yet you beat it so easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.52,0:05:07.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn’t easy.\NNot only that…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.26,0:05:12.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,During the battle, that Bount was\Ndefinitely acting strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.19,0:05:19.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He was even going easy on\Nhis attacks against the squad members…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.60,0:05:22.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to Kariya?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.81,0:05:27.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He seems to have gotten\Nsome unknown power.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.98,0:05:30.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I think he called it the “Jokai Crest.”
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.96,0:05:34.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He said he’s gonna blow up\NSeireitei with that power.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.09,0:05:39.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kariya’s actions were unusual\Neven for that other Bount?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.39,0:05:42.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If only we could’ve\Nstopped him then…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.50,0:05:45.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It’s over.\NNo use mulling over it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.06,0:05:49.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,By the way,\Nwhat happened to Ichinose?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.77,0:05:52.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We received word that\NCaptain Zaraki brought him down.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.30,0:05:57.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kurosaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.54,0:05:59.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, are you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.55,0:05:59.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.90,0:06:00.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Inoue!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.36,0:06:01.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kira!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.27,0:06:05.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Jidanbo’s injuries are taken care of,\Nso I came after you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.93,0:06:10.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It just so happened that Squad 3\Nmembers were guarding the gates.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.74,0:06:12.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So I brought her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.23,0:06:14.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.43,0:06:18.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to put you right to work,\Nbut can you tend to Ishida’s wounds?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.63,0:06:20.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.06,0:06:26.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Inoue, thank you…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.06,0:06:29.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t need to get back to 100%.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.65,0:06:32.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Just…can you do it quickly?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.97,0:06:34.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.81,0:06:36.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Rangiku?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.25,0:06:39.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ishida, weren’t you listening\Nto what’s been said?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.27,0:06:44.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I understand how anxious you are,\Nbut calm down a bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.39,0:06:45.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.76,0:06:48.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Rest is essential in a battle, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.92,0:06:52.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone’s been on the move\Nsince last night!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.64,0:06:54.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You’re right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.73,0:06:57.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If something happens,\Nwe’ll get word right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.90,0:06:59.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It’s no use getting anxious.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.28,0:07:11.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And who’s available now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.72,0:07:14.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir! Mainly Squad 11.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.53,0:07:16.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Since Squad 11 is without\Nits captain right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.58,0:07:18.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,they hadn’t received orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.74,0:07:21.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,They weren’t involved in\Nthe afternoon confusion,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.29,0:07:23.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,so they’re the healthiest squad\Naround right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.81,0:07:28.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That’s right, I hadn’t sent\Nany orders to Squad 11.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.44,0:07:37.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! I wanted to fight\Nthe Bounts myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.51,0:07:40.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I hear there’s only one left!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.06,0:07:43.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Same here!\NI wanted to pay them back
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.28,0:07:44.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,for what they did in\Nthe World of the Living.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.88,0:07:48.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And the captain just left\Nand hasn’t returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.95,0:07:51.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It seems he fought with\Na Soul Reaper named Ichinose
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.53,0:07:53.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,who sided with the Bounts.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.22,0:07:57.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He’s probably quite happy and\Nsightseeing in the Rukon District.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.09,0:07:59.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichinose, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.06,0:08:02.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I owed him some payback.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.33,0:08:07.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That bastard…!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.69,0:08:11.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well, the last one standing\Nis a bigwig.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.64,0:08:15.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll find this one with\Nmy own hands for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.23,0:08:16.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Reporting!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.14,0:08:18.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Seireitei… The North District…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.68,0:08:20.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There’s nothing suspicious\Nin any of the blocks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.39,0:08:24.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The other squads are exhausted\Nfrom the afternoon skirmish.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.52,0:08:27.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If we find him now,\Nwe get to do whatever we want!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.69,0:08:28.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So find him, no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.62,0:08:33.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We have an urgent message
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.57,0:08:37.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,from Captain Kyoraku of Squad 8\Nand Captain Ukitake of Squad 13.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.55,0:08:43.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn’t Captain Ukitake\Nin poor health?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.53,0:08:46.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I’m sorry, but he went\Nto the Central Library
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.74,0:08:48.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,in order to find data on the Bounts.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.05,0:08:51.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm… Well, no matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.98,0:08:54.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And what is this urgent message?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.05,0:08:57.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The data Rantao left behind\Nhas been discovered.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.66,0:09:01.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It has an entry about\Nan explosive power
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.63,0:09:04.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,that was sealed in the Jokai Crest.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.10,0:09:06.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.49,0:09:11.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Which means…\Nthat man, Kariya, wasn’t lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.23,0:09:13.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,According to the data,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.90,0:09:16.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,in order to totally draw out\Nthe power in the Jokai Crest…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.85,0:09:21.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,a short period of time is necessary\Nafter activating the Jokai Crest.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.17,0:09:24.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And how much time is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.61,0:09:26.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,About one day…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.56,0:09:29.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So that’s what Kariya meant
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.07,0:09:33.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,when he said everything will\Nbe decided in one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.65,0:09:34.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.05,0:09:36.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.64,0:09:39.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,To think he’d even use that\Nas a part of his tactics.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.43,0:09:42.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We must not let down\Nour guard against him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.85,0:09:47.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We must take this Kariya\Ninto custody quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.15,0:09:50.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I will send directives to each squad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.43,0:09:55.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It seems we don’t even have time\Nfor a captains’ meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.16,0:09:55.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.04,0:09:59.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Tell Captain Ukitake\Nand Captain Kyoraku
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.20,0:10:01.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,to continue checking the data.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.64,0:10:02.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Understood, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.06,0:10:15.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Soi Fon’s recovery\Nwas slower than expected,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.90,0:10:17.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,so she is on standby at her quarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.92,0:10:18.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.94,0:10:23.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Kurotsuchi’s ability to return\Nto battle is also very questionable.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.01,0:10:27.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Captains Kyoraku and Ukitake\Nhave secluded themselves
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.69,0:10:29.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,in the Central Library\Nto gather information.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.61,0:10:31.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What of Captain Komamura?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.43,0:10:34.87,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He is guarding\NGeneral Captain Yamamoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.08,0:10:37.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,All right. I understand the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.43,0:10:39.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.19,0:10:41.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you. If you’ll excuse me…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.98,0:10:43.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Isane!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.24,0:10:44.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Rangiku?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.50,0:10:46.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you taste my cooking!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.60,0:10:48.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’m still on duty…!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.19,0:10:50.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying\Nyou won’t eat my cooking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.22,0:11:29.83,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Who’s there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.73,0:11:48.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You’re…!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.19,0:11:52.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Rantao!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.82,0:11:57.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A gun that fires kido?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.53,0:12:17.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How did you find me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.98,0:12:19.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A Bount sensor?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.62,0:12:24.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Right. I’m the one that knows\Nthe most about Bounts.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.16,0:12:26.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why haven’t you given that\Ntechnology to the Soul Reapers?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.77,0:12:32.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Because…I intend to settle\Neverything by myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.14,0:12:35.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Interesting thing you have there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.09,0:12:39.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like it packs a punch,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.17,0:12:42.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,but it’s not enough to bring me down.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.66,0:12:45.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What’s the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.92,0:12:51.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That mark…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.21,0:12:54.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible…!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.81,0:13:06.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,After the konpaku experiment failed,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.02,0:13:09.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,we were sent to\Nthe World of the Living.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.43,0:13:11.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shortly before our arrival,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.56,0:13:13.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,there were reports in\Nthe World of the Living about
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.77,0:13:17.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,a large number of humans\Npossessing strange powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.65,0:13:20.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,They were Bounts.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.38,0:13:24.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The Bounts were confused\Nabout their strength,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.09,0:13:28.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,yet they tried to live among\Nthe normal humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.08,0:13:35.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But due to their strength,\Nthey weren’t able to remain friendly
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.22,0:13:37.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,with humans for long periods of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.61,0:13:41.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And finally, they began\Nto be persecuted.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.39,0:13:52.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I tried to get close to the Bounts\Nin order to save them…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.43,0:13:58.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Because they were victims\Nof our experiments.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.98,0:14:04.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Do not fear me.\NI am your friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.49,0:14:10.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I rounded up the Bounts
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.84,0:14:14.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and advised them to\Nstay together and hide.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.81,0:14:18.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I will return to Soul Society\Nand make arrangements so that
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.29,0:14:22.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,you will be under the protection\Nof Soul Society.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.85,0:14:24.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Is that possible…?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.66,0:14:28.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. It’s true that this will\Nnot be an easy task.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.90,0:14:32.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It will probably take several years
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.77,0:14:35.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,before protection of the Bounts\Nbecomes a reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.85,0:14:37.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.48,0:14:41.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We will wait here until you return.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.58,0:14:52.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But something totally unexpected\Nawaited me
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.45,0:14:54.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,when I returned to Soul Society.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.65,0:15:03.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The Central 46 of that time\Ndecided that everything
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.01,0:15:04.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,regarding the konpaku experiment
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.62,0:15:11.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,as well as its by-product, the Bounts,\Nwould be buried in secrecy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.52,0:15:16.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you going to turn\Nyour backs on the Bounts?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.35,0:15:21.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We acknowledge that\Nthe konpaku experiment was inhumane.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.66,0:15:25.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If you believe that,\Nwhy won’t you save them?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.76,0:15:28.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,They possess amazing power!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.61,0:15:29.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If we ignore them,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.70,0:15:32.87,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,they may even become\Na danger to Soul Society!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.06,0:15:36.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Bounts who cannot control reishi
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.20,0:15:38.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,cannot pass through the Dangai,\NPrecipice World.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.06,0:15:44.83,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,They will never be a threat\Nto Soul Society. However…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.04,0:15:48.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That is not the case in\Nthe World of the Living.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.43,0:15:52.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Our duty is to regulate\Nthe balance of konpaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.63,0:15:55.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There is a possibility the Bounts\Nthreaten that equilibrium.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.85,0:16:00.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You don’t mean the Bounts will be…?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.39,0:16:07.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Do you actually believe\Nsuch a thing can be allowed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.37,0:16:09.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No, we don’t.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.43,0:16:11.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We must live with the burden\Nof our mistake
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.61,0:16:16.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and strive to never repeat\Nsuch a mistake again!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.39,0:16:22.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot…I cannot turn my back\Non the Bounts!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.43,0:16:33.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Take them all into custody!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.95,0:16:35.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kill any who resist!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.07,0:16:38.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.71,0:16:50.83,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,In order to save the Bounts,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.95,0:16:52.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I went to the World of the Living\Nwithout permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.05,0:16:56.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There are still comrades further inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.72,0:16:57.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.70,0:17:01.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll do something.\NGo on and get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.34,0:17:02.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.67,0:17:24.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey you! Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.98,0:17:32.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.67,0:17:37.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Aren’t you…Rantao?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.69,0:17:40.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.07,0:17:44.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Rantao… You belong to\Nthe Bount Investigation Unit!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.56,0:17:47.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The Investigation Unit has already\Nreturned to Soul Society.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.66,0:17:49.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.10,0:17:53.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,She’s running away!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.18,0:17:55.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Where do you think you’re going?!\NAfter her!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.43,0:18:05.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,She’s a traitor!\NAfter her! After her!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.92,0:18:22.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I will distract the Soul Reapers,\Nso you must escape during that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.43,0:18:23.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.18,0:18:26.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If you go outside,\Nthere are sure to be other Bounts.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.78,0:18:28.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Run away with your comrades.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.43,0:18:31.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But then you…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.25,0:18:32.83,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll be fine…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.80,0:18:35.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.92,0:18:41.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The Bounts have much more power\Nhidden within them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.56,0:18:44.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This will help to draw out that power.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.66,0:18:47.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’m really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.68,0:18:49.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You’ll be forced to\Nendure suffering now,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.85,0:18:51.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,but I’m sure one day…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.30,0:18:53.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So you must live!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.58,0:18:55.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Over this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.60,0:18:56.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t let her get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.52,0:18:59.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now! Run up those stairs\Nand get outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.98,0:19:07.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, I was captured\Nand taken to Soul Society.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.19,0:19:12.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And Seireitei held me\Nsolely responsible
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.03,0:19:13.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and put a seal on the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.81,0:19:17.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Subsequently, the Bounts\Ntook advantage
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.38,0:19:20.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,of the powers hidden in\Nthe item I gave the boy,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.33,0:19:23.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and perfected the method\Nof controlling dolls.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.73,0:19:28.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,With their new power,\Nthe Bounts planned their revenge
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.74,0:19:32.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and tried to attack Soul Society\Ncountless times.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.18,0:19:36.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,However, they were rejected\Neach time by the Soul Reapers
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.62,0:19:38.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and their numbers dwindled\Nto almost nothing…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.36,0:19:42.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and even the record of their existence\Nwas erased from Seireitei.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.99,0:19:50.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But I have never forgotten the Bounts.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.43,0:19:54.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Then you came to Soul Society.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.85,0:20:00.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You are that boy…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.56,0:20:03.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.64,0:20:07.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How you got that mark?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.02,0:20:10.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That mark is sure to have appeared
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.24,0:20:12.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,when you activated\Na certain item.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.06,0:20:16.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The one who gave you\Nthat item was me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.85,0:20:20.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I have lived to save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.47,0:20:24.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There is no Soul Reaper remaining\Nwho remembers the past!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.61,0:20:26.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Soul Society has changed, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.94,0:20:28.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now, I can…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.80,0:20:30.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What a thing to bring up now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.01,0:20:31.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It’s not a lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.78,0:20:33.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If you use the power\Nof the Jokai Crest
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.62,0:20:35.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,which was sealed in the Seireitei…!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.56,0:20:37.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The power of the Jokai Crest?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.81,0:20:41.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I absorbed that energy into\Nmy body long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.76,0:20:42.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.72,0:20:45.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll use that power to destroy\Nthe Soul Reapers.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.14,0:20:46.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.12,0:20:58.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This Spiritual Pressure is\Ncoming from Rantao!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.99,0:21:00.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Is she in a battle?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.75,0:21:03.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The only Bount remaining is Kariya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.36,0:21:07.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So Kariya is sure to be\Nwhere Rantao is!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.02,0:21:13.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever action you planned\Nis too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.06,0:21:17.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The only Bount remaining is me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.58,0:21:20.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it’s only you,\NI will save you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.57,0:21:24.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So stupid! You created Bounts.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.32,0:21:26.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I intended to deal with you after\Nyou had seen Seireitei destroyed
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.69,0:21:30.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and repented for what you had done.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.64,0:21:33.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But you can die right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.37,0:22:16.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You always lament on\Nhow boring this town is
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.04,0:22:20.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,…Searching for a place in the sun
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.62,0:22:25.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The melody you hum is that\Nrusty, same old song
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.30,0:22:29.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,…Rejecting any new song
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.45,0:22:38.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're anxious because somewhere\Nin your heart, you believe in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.43,0:22:40.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Baby, it's you;
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.53,0:22:47.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That pain will eventually become\Na memory
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.92,0:22:49.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're the only one.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.92,0:22:57.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't think, just feel,\Nlet your whole body tremble;
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.52,0:22:59.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,future is you!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.48,0:23:01.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Baby, it's me;
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.63,0:23:08.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're never alone, I'm right here
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.82,0:23:10.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We should be as one;
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.90,0:23:14.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you stumble, I don’t mind
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.69,0:23:21.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I want to tell you now\Nabout the thing called love
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.74,0:23:25.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ishida suddenly disappeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.35,0:23:26.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s go find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.12,0:23:29.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We don’t know when\Na Quincy arrow will explode.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.33,0:23:31.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What if we find it the instant\Nbefore it blows up?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.41,0:23:33.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We’ll forget it and run far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.59,0:23:34.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.53,0:23:37.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Horrible things just flow\Nright out of your mouths, don’t they?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.71,0:23:49.70,On Top,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Illustrated Guide to Soul Reapers\NGolden after these messages.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.73,0:23:50.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Illustrated Guide to Soul Reapers!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.88,0:23:52.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’m hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.25,0:23:53.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,All right, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.32,0:23:56.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Squad 10’s famous specialty!\NJust made!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.02,0:23:57.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Come and eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.29,0:23:58.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.10,0:24:01.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Just as you requested, Orihime,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.09,0:24:03.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I made lots of bean paste dishes, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.41,0:24:05.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.60,0:24:06.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This stinks!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.72,0:24:09.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Don’t just stand there.\NHurry up and take your portion!
